message: Hello Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would significantly benefit your business. Given its value and the impact it could have on your operations, I am offering it to you for $14,000. This price reflects its high quality and the potential return on investment it offers. I am confident that this product will exceed your expectations and contribute positively to your company's growth. Please let me know if you have any questions or need further information. I look forward to the opportunity to serve your business needs.
